structurednavigation-desc: Describes the purpose of the StructuredNavigation extension
structurednavigation-separator-symbol: Defines the symbol/character that should be used for separating each link in a navigation.
structurednavigation-reserved-username: Defines the username that's reserved by this extension for doing automated tasks.
structurednavigation-view-emptystate-tit: The title shown for the empty state screen when a user visits a navigation that doesn't exist yet.
structurednavigation-view-emptystate-sum: The summary shown for the empty state screen when a user visits a navigation that doesn't exist yet.
structurednavigation-view-emptystate-but: The button label shown on the empty state screen when a user visits a navigation that doesn't exist yet.
